{"id": "1521197584482570461", "channel_id": "1521197584482570461", "author_id": "143371823680192512", "author_name": "yu__kun", "content": "Hi there,\nI'm a new player (started ~2 week ago, little less) and I use currently the team : Thais, ghelot, saya and Aigis for campaign (actually at chapt 6)\n\nI don't really struggle most of the time but I don't know what to think of this team because i'm always like 20-30hp left at the end of the last boss and sometime (most of the time honnestly hahaha) I begin the boss at 25% hp (~100hp).\nI link the images of all units I have and wheels (all R wheel are +12 so I didn't include them)\n\nHere my questions :\n- What team would you recommend me to do for the rest of the campaing? I try using salvador instead of ghelot but doesn't feel smooth or good and I can up to lvl50 any unit because I have enough ressource\n\n- Should I continue pulling for character or should I switch to wheels with the free currencies ? I actually switch to wheel to try to have +12 blade of the Titan for my dps but don't know if it's the right choice\n\n- Should I pull Pontos? I was thinking of pulling pontos and having dupes of other char if failing because I like his def down kit that I don't really have a unit for this roles but I'm hesitant to wait for the next unit annoucement before deciding. I have 210 pull currently\n\nReally appreciate all the help or advices you'll give 😄", "timestamp": "2026-06-29T16:56:06.625000+00:00", "thread_id": "1521197584482570461", "attachments": [{"id": "1521197584914579506", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1718308, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1521197584482570461/1521197584914579506/image.png?ex=6a43f526&is=6a42a3a6&hm=fcab1f8cf95b8b2f6fab4d11bfb149957aa8a4c4660ae36a7a4370720220fec7&"}, {"id": "1521197585434415295", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1673363, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1521197584482570461/1521197585434415